Write the constructor method in the NurbsSurface class.
Remember to respond with a snippet in the form of the following:
```
class NurbsSurface {
    constructor(controlPoints, weights, knotsU, knotsV) {
        // your code here
    }
}
```

```javascript
class NurbsSurface {
    constructor(controlPoints, weights, knotsU, knotsV) {
        this.controlPoints = controlPoints;
        this.weights = weights;
        this.knotsU = knotsU;
        this.knotsV = knotsV;
        this.uDegree = knotsU.length - 1 - this.controlPoints.length;
        this.vDegree = knotsV.length - 1 - this.controlPoints[0].length;
        this.dimension = 3;

    }
}
```
